metadata.description: 300 Founding members of the DAO is a mulitcultural group of likeminded individuals who desire to do good and truly impact this world. Their support and contributions to this project have been memorialized by an exclusive Founders Digital Member Card for the DAO. These Founding members have a deep knowledge of business, technology, and finance, and have dedicated their time to identify and secure partnerships and ventures for the DAO members to participate in and benefit from. The Founding members will receive a small revenue share from each successful project taken on by the DAO. With a maximum of 1 million members and only 300 of these ever minted... these Exclusive NFTs are the Spartans of the DAO.
metadata.name: D8A DAO Founder #1
